title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Live A Superyacht Life with Lavish Rewards
content:
Set sail in A Superyacht Life this week and be rewarded handsomely with 5X GTA$ and RP. Go to the bridge of your Galaxy Super Yacht or dial up Captain Darcy to get under way, or begin your nautical adventures with a 40% discount on any Galaxy model at DockTease.

Completing three A Superyacht Life Missions will accomplish the Weekly Challenge, landing you the Vibrant Check Smoking Jacket in addition to GTA$100,000.
